channel.title: Project Annihilation Help, how to change afk time?
channel.description: Hey guys, i just wana know how to change this... When people are afk doing something they end up logging out becuase they've ben afk to long just like every server but mine, they log out like in 60 seconds, which gets really annoying if you are afk for a short amount of time. i need help changing this please help!

item.title: Project Annihilation Help, how to change afk time?
item.dc:creator: @kronixz kronikz
item.description:
@kronixz wrote:

Can you post the command? If you don’t have the SystemTimeMillis on a large amount of time, it’ll log out.
